snippet.title: Amber Full Movie | Raj Kapoor Old Hindi Movie | Nargis | Old Classic Hindi Movie
snippet.description:
Old Hindi Movie Amber (1952) 
Starring : Nargis, Raj Kapoor , Tanuja, Cuckoo, Helen, Tun Tun.
Producer : Seth Jagat Narain, Director: Jayant Desai

Synopsis : Amber stars the hottest screen pair of the time in the lead, Raj Kapoor and Nargis.
Backed by the title role, Nargis portrayed Amber a princess born from a secret marriage between a Prince and a village belle from the hill regions of a supposed kingdom. After the death of her parents under suspicious circumstances, Amber grew up among the village folks unaware of her origin. However once in her youth, the fact is revealed to her and she vows to avenge the death of her parents.
However circumstances and vicious designs of those in power suppresses her efforts. On the way Amber finds solace in the arms of a hero, Raj (Raj Kapoor) who joins her in her efforts along with his sidekick Veenu (Agha).
How the three together finally achieve their goal makes for an adventurous-musical viewing that is both entertaining and nostalgic.
